long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extensions helps you easily lookup definitions of words in free online dictionaries/thesaurus.

Current version of the extension includes Cambridge Advanced Learner's dictionary, Oxford Advanced Learner's dictionary, Collins English Dictionary, Online Etymology Dictionary, and many more.

You may contact the developer if you wish to add a dictionary of your choice to this browser extension.
